text.section:
The Supreme Court shall require, at a minimum, the following:
A process for reviewing the objective criteria for evidence-based practices established by the vendor or contractor providing the program;
A process for auditing the effectiveness of the program;
An opportunity for programs that do not meet the criteria based on the audit results to improve performance; and
A mechanism to defund any program provided by a vendor or contractor that does not meet the criteria upon a second audit.
